{"tid":732514,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Facebook貼美國《獨立宣言》 竟被視為「仇恨言論」刪除","createTime":"2018-07-07T03:48:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-07T04:10:55.000Z","uid":39464,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"7980fd30e17d08ec51e3f89872bd6c2646f56263","tid":732514,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T03:48:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpxRwkcH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpxRwkcH.jpg&h=ee2b3df9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本週適逢美國國慶日，大大小小慶祝活動不斷，但近來致力於管控仇恨言論的臉書，竟將美國極為重要的《獨立宣言》視為仇恨言論，將其刪除。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，位於德州利柏提的地方報紙，為了慶祝7月4日美國國慶日，以分段的方式將《獨立宣言》PO上臉書，其中一個段落寫道，「他在我們中間煽動內亂，並且竭力挑唆那些殘酷無情、沒有開化的印第安人來殺掠我們追撞的居民；而眾所周知，印第安人的作戰規律是不分男女老幼，一律格殺勿論的。」遭臉書視為仇恨言論刪除。<br />\n<br />\n臉書發言人表示，將《獨立宣言》刪除是一項錯誤，認為應該是「沒有開化的印第安人」一詞抵觸臉書的審查機制，臉書也在發現錯誤後第一時間恢復該則貼文，並向該份報紙道歉。臉書強調，他們每週必須處理數百萬則貼文，難免會有出錯的時候。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2480896\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2480896&d=bfsb2Z%2BflDqDUoBqCQS%2FZv755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=b15c1e48\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2480896&h=c0afc718\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2480896</a>"},{"pid":"257b583f7fded6c4beaa24a0589bf29cc0e7db23","tid":732514,"uid":77196,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T03:50:12.000Z","msg":"豬西伯格 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40e23584564544fe52cfa9c5d9e1773bba492d3c","tid":732514,"uid":59030,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T03:50:17.000Z","msg":"他在我們中間煽動內亂<br />\n邊個他?"},{"pid":"d567fdbbee98763ed06930d277df09f726dc6fce","tid":732514,"uid":177089,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T03:51:23.000Z","msg":"左膠"},{"pid":"2d9c4150b7327c065e61a2fd7ecff1c10aea497e","tid":732514,"uid":6799,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"40e23584564544fe52cfa9c5d9e1773bba492d3c","tid":732514,"uid":59030,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T03:50:17.000Z","msg":"他在我們中間煽動內亂<br />\n邊個他?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T03:52:10.000Z","msg":"個陣指英國"},{"pid":"85eed1576804710370c6e4b8972223795bf524ea","tid":732514,"uid":98386,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T03:52:55.000Z","msg":"垃圾FB講句支那都ban一個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ec0a04ff5cde9eb745e5a697a9b611c502b25bb","tid":732514,"uid":85461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T03:53:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/07/115303_c69ce76ff054c10d5f57aad2de4fe5ad.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F07%2F115303_c69ce76ff054c10d5f57aad2de4fe5ad.gif&h=daa52a4c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7ccce20db4ba187da62fe8734290bde31601eebf","tid":732514,"uid":22566,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T04:01:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 喂 豬西 睇個款似諗住係中國落地生根喎"},{"pid":"ac49fe903e395e6b2d95dcb5c98077ee424deacf","tid":732514,"uid":59030,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T04:03:14.000Z","msg":"應該立即以叛國罪拘捕豬閪伯格"},{"pid":"bb540111c6a9861c82d1bf070973c9161a0c6fc3","tid":732514,"uid":70227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T04:03:54.000Z","msg":"唔認祖國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.